<p>
  Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,
</p>

<p>
  Thanks for signing up to Blendergrid! You're one short step away from your
  first render: uploading a .blend file.
</p>

<p>
  Here's a quick walkthrough that shows how it works:
</p>

<p>
  <a href="https://youtu.be/LPpWWvtNCXg">
    <img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/LPpWWvtNCXg/maxresdefault.jpg"
         alt="Watch the Blendergrid walkthrough" width="480"
         style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 8px;">
  </a>
</p>

<p>
  When you're ready, upload your first .blend file:
</p>

<p>
  <a href="<%= new_upload_url(session_token: @session_token) %>"
     style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 22px; background: #101828;
            color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;">
    Upload your .blend file
  </a>
</p>

<p>
  Happy rendering,<br>
  the Blendergrid team
</p>

<p>
  <a href="https://www.blendergrid.com">www.blendergrid.com</a>
</p>
